{"tid":281589,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隔住個mon都覺得臭）84年奧運MJ波鞋150萬賣出","createTime":"2017-06-12T23:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T00:58:04.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dec0402ad4b4d396505601686079186f6ba72921","tid":281589,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T23:44:00.000Z","msg":"「籃球之神」米高佐敦雖然退咗休好耐，但佢幾時都係大眾焦點，而喺美國時間星期日，佢喺1984年洛杉磯奧運決賽所著嘅波鞋就以190,373美金（約150萬港元），創出咗比賽著過波鞋嘅拍賣價新紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n呢對創出拍賣新紀錄嘅Converse波鞋，係MJ喺洛杉磯奧運美國贏西班牙嗰場決賽所著嘅波鞋，鞋上面有MJ簽名，拍賣價由10,000美金開始，結果由一個當年奧運得11歲嘅場邊執波仔以190,373美金投到。至於著過嘅波鞋拍賣價上一個嘅紀錄，亦都係由MJ所保持，嗰一對係佢喺1997年NBA總決賽公牛對爵士Game 5、病住都入38分嗰場幫公牛贏波嗰「Flu Game」所著嘅 AJ波鞋，2013年創出嘅拍賣價係104,765美金。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497244699_60e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497244699_60e3.jpg&h=b1b7ee4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"080c8344a9b3e9c9a1811294a15788dae746fe53","tid":281589,"uid":37747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T23:51:30.000Z","msg":"係香港實比阿媽拎左去洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b0f80a8ce6454e27a577f514c5218d711c0a2f","tid":281589,"uid":9021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T23:54:08.000Z","msg":"原味波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebb80d68e6980e9afe6757a694f8890e631daef","tid":281589,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T00:06:18.000Z","msg":"98%new<br />\n買番黎淨係著過一次<br />\n地鐵沿線交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df6c741264d0cd8443aae503b2173ee3758c779","tid":281589,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T00:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>98%new<br />\n買番黎淨係著過一次<br />\n地鐵沿線交收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"